{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Object.values()","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/values","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects\">Standard built-in objects</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\"><code>Object</code></a></strong></li><li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>Propriedades</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/constructor\"><code>Object.prototype.constructor</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/proto\"><code>Object.prototype.__proto__</code></a></li></ol></li><li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>Métodos</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineGetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/assign\"><code>Object.assign()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/create\"><code>Object.create()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/defineProperties\"><code>Object.defineProperties()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/defineProperty\"><code>Object.defineProperty()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/entries\"><code>Object.entries()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/freeze\"><code>Object.freeze()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/fromEntries\"><code>Object.fromEntries()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/getOwnPropertyDescriptor\"><code>Object.getOwnPropertyDescriptor()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/getOwnPropertyDescriptors\"><code>Object.getOwnPropertyDescriptors()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/getOwnPropertyNames\"><code>Object.getOwnPropertyNames()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/getOwnPropertySymbols\"><code>Object.getOwnPropertySymbols()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/getPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.getPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwn\"><code>Object.hasOwn()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/is\"><code>Object.is()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isExtensible\"><code>Object.isExtensible()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isFrozen\"><code>Object.isFrozen()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isSealed\"><code>Object.isSealed()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/keys\"><code>Object.keys()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/preventExtensions\"><code>Object.preventExtensions()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/seal\"><code>Object.seal()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li><li><em><code>Object.values()</code></em></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"> <div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>Esta é uma <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tecnologia experimental (en-US)</a></strong><br>Verifique a <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">tabela de compatibilidade entre Navegadores</a> cuidadosamente antes de usar essa funcionalidade em produção.</p></div></div>\n\n<p>O método&nbsp;<code><strong>Object.values()</strong></code>&nbsp;retorna um&nbsp;array com os valores das&nbsp;propriedades de um&nbsp;dado&nbsp;objeto, na mesma ordem provida pelo&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Statements/for...in\"><code>for...in</code></a> laço (sendo&nbsp;a diferença que o laço&nbsp;for-in também enumera&nbsp;as propriedades na cadeia prototype).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxe","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">Object.values(<var>obj</var>)</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parâmetros","title":"Parâmetros","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"obj\"><code>obj</code></dt>\n <dd>O objeto cujos valores das&nbsp;propriedades enumeradas&nbsp;serão retornados.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"valor_de_retorno","title":"Valor de retorno","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Um array contendo os valores das propriedades enumeradas do dado objeto.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"descrição","title":"Descrição","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>Object.values()</code> retorna um array cujos elementos são os valores das propriedades enumeradas encontradas no objeto. A ordem das propriedades é a mesma que a dada pelo laço sobre os valores da&nbsp;propriedade do objeto manualmente.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplos","title":"Exemplos","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> obj <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">foo</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"bar\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">baz</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">42</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Object<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">values</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>obj<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// ['bar', 42]</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// array como objeto</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> obj <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'a'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'b'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'c'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Object<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">values</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>obj<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// ['a', 'b', 'c']</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// array como objeto com ordenação de chave aleatória</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> an_obj <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'a'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'b'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">7</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'c'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Object<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">values</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>an_obj<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// ['b', 'c', 'a']</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// getFoo é a propriedade a qual não é enumerável</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> my_obj <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Object<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">create</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">getFoo</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">value</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>foo<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nmy_obj<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>foo <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"bar\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Object<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">values</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>my_obj<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// ['bar']</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// argumento não-objeto será coagido num objeto</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Object<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">values</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"foo\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// ['f', 'o', 'o']</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"biblioteca_de_suporte","title":"Biblioteca de Suporte","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code><font face=\"Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif\">Para adicionar&nbsp;compatibilidade ao suporte de&nbsp;&nbsp;</font>Object.values</code> em ambientes antigos que nativamente não o suportam, você pode encontrar uma biblioteca de suporte&nbsp;nos repositórios&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/tc39/proposal-object-values-entries\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">tc39/proposal-object-values-entries</a> ou no&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/es-shims/Object.values\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">es-shims/Object.values</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificações</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Situação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-object.values\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'Object.values' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect3\"><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect4\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect5\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div></div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Aspecto</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td>51.0 [1]</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/47\" title=\"Released on 2016-06-07.\">47</a> (47)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span> [2]</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Aspecto</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Android Webview</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n   <th>Chrome para Android</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>51.0 [1]</td>\n   <td>47.0 (47)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>51.0 [1]</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>[1] Por trás de uma&nbsp;flag.</p>\n\n<p>[2] Ver&nbsp;<a href=\"https://bugs.webkit.org/show_bug.cgi?id=150131\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">bug 150131</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ver_também","title":"Ver&nbsp;também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Enumerability_and_ownership_of_properties\">Enumerability and ownership of properties</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/keys\"><code>Object.keys()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/entries\"><code>Object.entries()</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/create\"><code>Object.create()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/getOwnPropertyNames\"><code>Object.getOwnPropertyNames()</code></a></li>\n</ul>","titleAsText":"Ver também"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxe","id":"sintaxe"},{"text":"Descrição","id":"descrição"},{"text":"Exemplos","id":"exemplos"},{"text":"Biblioteca de Suporte","id":"biblioteca_de_suporte"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Ver&nbsp;também","id":"ver_também"}],"summary":"O método Object.values() retorna um array com os valores das propriedades de um dado objeto, na mesma ordem provida pelo for...in laço (sendo a diferença que o laço for-in também enumera as propriedades na cadeia prototype).","popularity":0.0032,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Object.values()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Object.values()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Object.values()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Object.values()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Object.values()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Object.values()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Object.values()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Object.values()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)